{
  "texts": [
    "Through a systematic examination of their outputs and decision-making processes, this research aims to identify methodologies and frameworks that can enhance the interpretability and explainability of LLMs.",
    "By doing so, it seeks to contribute to the development of AI technologies that are not only technologically advanced but also ethically responsible and socially acceptable.The main contributions of our study include:1.",
    "Conducted a comprehensive evaluation of interpretability and explainability across five leading Large Language Models: TripoSR, Gemma-7b, Mistral 7B, Llama-2-7b, and GemMoE-Beta-1, utilizing a novel combination of qualitative and quantitative benchmarks. 2.",
    "Identified key strengths and limitations in the current approaches to enhancing transparency and understandability in LLMs, highlighting areas where each model excels and falls short. 3.",
    "Proposed a set of criteria for assessing the interpretability and explainability of LLMs, contributing to the standardization of evaluation methodologies in the field of AI. 4."
  ]
}